33-0.query:
SELECT MIN(cn1.name) AS first_company, MIN(cn2.name) AS second_company, MIN(mi_idx1.info) AS first_rating, MIN(mi_idx2.info) AS second_rating, MIN(t1.title) AS first_movie, MIN(t2.title) AS second_movie
 FROM cat_company_name_4 AS cn1,
 cat_company_name_4 AS cn2,
 cat_info_type_4 AS it1,
 cat_info_type_4 AS it2,
 cat_kind_type_4 AS kt1,
 cat_kind_type_4 AS kt2,
 cat_movie_companies_4 AS mc1,
 cat_movie_companies_4 AS mc2,
 cat_movie_info_idx_4 AS mi_idx1,
 cat_movie_info_idx_4 AS mi_idx2,
 cat_title_4 AS t1,
 cat_title_4 AS t2
 WHERE it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id 
AND t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id
AND kt1.id = t1.kind_id
AND cn1.id = mc1.company_id
AND t1.id = mc1.movie_id 
AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id
AND it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id
AND t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id
AND kt2.id = t2.kind_id
AND cn2.id = mc2.company_id
AND t2.id = mc2.movie_id
AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id
AND cn1.country_code = '@param0'
AND it1.info = '@param1'
AND it2.info = '@param2'
AND kt1.kind IN ('@param3')
AND kt2.kind IN ('@param4')
AND mi_idx2.info < '@param5'
AND t2.production_year BETWEEN @param6 AND @param7;
